RE|REG|A1082044|1302959|2702654|FCC|08/03/2017|5|3.	Upon the completion of the environmental notification process and all required environmental review, Applicant shall complete the Part 2 certification of the second ASR application.  Upon grant of this second ASR application, Applicant will request
