RE|REG|A1154650|1304272|2703968|FCC|11/29/2017|0|On December 9, 2017, Verizon Wireless (VAW) LLC (Applicant) filed Antenna Structure Registration (ASR) Application No. A1057974 for a 53.3 meter (175 foot) lattice tower in Oak Grove, Montana.  National notice was published via the Commission’s ASR system
RE|REG|A1154650|1304272|2703968|FCC|11/29/2017|1|on March 10, 2017.  On February 14, 2017, Mr. Randall McClain filed a Request for Further Environmental Processing (Request) to express his concerns “as to the obstruction the saturation an additional communication tower…will pose” at the proposed new
