RE|REG|A1281100|1327395|2727736|FCC|02/29/2024|4|determined to be 11 feet above mean sea level. TowerCom will install equipment cabinets on an elevated steel platform with the bottom of the cabinets at an elevation of 12 feet 4 inches. If security lights are used, TowerCom has agreed to install down
