RE|REG|A1312144|1327665|2728006|FCC|04/05/2024|2|Certification, to minimize impacts to the 0.09 acre of wetland associated with the proposed project. The equipment will be elevated one foot above base flood elevation. Construction should be completed by June 5, 2024, in accordance with the building
RE|REG|A1312144|1327665|2728006|FCC|04/05/2024|3|permit issued by Baldwin County, Alabama. Further, if security lights are used, Tillman has agreed to further minimize potential impacts on migratory birds by installing down-shielded, motion-sensor security lighting.
