RE|REG|A1298953|1327692|2728033|FCC|04/11/2024|2|conditions, as well as the State of Louisiana Department of Environmental Quality Water Quality Certification WQC 200929-01. Work must be completed before October 8, 2024, when the Lafourche Paris Government permit expires. Additionally, Tillman has
