RE|REG|A1307319|1327708|2728049|FCC|04/15/2024|2|between May 1 and July 15, the maternity/pup season for the tricolored bat. Further, Bastrop County has agreed to implement the recommendations outlined in the August 20, 2023 Texas Parks and Wildlife Department letter. Finally, Bastrop County will
RE|REG|A1307319|1327708|2728049|FCC|04/15/2024|3|provide archaeological monitoring of all ground disturbing activities in the vicinity of the Alta Vista Cemetery, in accordance with the October 24, 2023 Texas Historical Commission letter.
