RE|REG|A1342124|1327998|2728339|FCC|05/24/2024|1|This FONSI is granted subject to all conditions and requirements contained in the record, including the use of visual bird diverters on guy wires and the use of down-shielded and motion activated security lighting. VB Nimbus would complete construction
