RE|REG|A1316835|1328045|2728386|FCC|06/03/2024|0|NEPA resolved per FONSI letter granted May 8, 2024, file number A1221065.
RE|REG|A1316835|1328045|2728386|FCC|06/03/2024|1|This FONSI is granted subject to all conditions and requirements contained in the record, including the US Fish and Wildlife Service’s conservation measures of clearing trees only between October 15 – March 31 to minimize impacts to the Indiana bat and
RE|REG|A1316835|1328045|2728386|FCC|06/03/2024|2|the northern long-eared bat. Additionally, Tillman will comply with conditions in Alabama Department of Transportation permit number 2-1-10696 dated April 29, 2024, which requires construction to be completed before April 18, 2025. Furthermore, if
