RE|REG|A1351389|1333067|2733578|FCC|03/27/2026|2|of Natural Resources on July 18, 2025. WEC will also only use down-shielded minimum intensity security lighting on all ground facilities. Finally, if vegetation clearing is proposed during the bobolink nesting season (May 20 - July 31), WEC will perform
