RE|REG|A1348367|1333291|2733802|FCC|04/15/2026|6|with the conditions in U.S. Army Corps of Engineers Nationwide Permit 57, the South Florida Water Management District Individual Environmental Resource Permit (that includes the Water Quality Certification and Coastal Zone Consistency Determination), and
RE|REG|A1348367|1333291|2733802|FCC|04/15/2026|7|the requirements of Collier County for Areas of Critical State Concern.
